Type: Package
Package: CatastRoNav
Title: Interface to the 'INSPIRE' Services of the Cadastre of Navarre
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Diego", "Hernangómez", , "diego.hernangomezherrero@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8457-4658")),
    person("Francisco J.", "Goerlich", role = "ctb",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1626-525X"))
  )
Description: Provides access to public spatial data from the Cadastre of
    Navarre through its 'INSPIRE' Atom feeds, Web Feature Service and Web
    Map Service endpoints. Supports complete municipal dataset downloads,
    bounding box feature queries and georeferenced map image downloads for
    addresses, buildings and cadastral parcels.
